title: RHOSLC Through This Recap
itunes:title: RHOSLC Through This Recap
description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which features the return of Kevin the driver AND the legendary travel bus. Seth also celebrates his rooftop Birthday, Brooks tries oysters, and Whitney presents a bubbie cake to her friend's husband.
